---
// Hero section — generous whitespace, centered text, no decoration
---

<section class="py-32 md:py-48 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-foggy-bg">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 md:px-8 text-center">
    <h1 class="font-bold tracking-tight text-foggy-ink" style="font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px); line-height: 1.1;">
      AI inference, run locally,<br class="hidden sm:block" /> in your country.
    </h1>

    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-[20px] leading-relaxed text-foggy-ink-light">
      Foggy runs open-source AI models on standard office hardware in emerging markets. No cloud markup. No cross-border data transfer. Native Swahili, Kinyarwanda, and English support — running on machines you control.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="#cta"
        class="rounded-lg bg-foggy-teal px-5 py-3 font-bold text-white hover:bg-foggy-teal-dark transition-colors"
      >
        Request a pilot
      </a>
      <a
        href="#evidence"
        class="rounded-lg px-5 py-3 font-bold text-foggy-ink hover:bg-foggy-bg transition-colors"
      >
        See it run
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-[14px] italic text-foggy-ink-light">
      Built in Cambridge, MA &middot; Pilot programs in Nairobi, Kigali, Addis
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
